  ## roll

  Tells Sphero to roll at a specific speed, along a specific heading.

  Heading is considered relative to the last calibrated position.


  ### Params


  - **speed** (<code>Number</code>)


  - **heading** (<code>Number</code>)


  - **state** (<code>Number</code>)


  ### Returns

  - (<code>null</code>)

